# Cursor project rules

- Always run `python manage.py makemigrations` after modifying Django models.
- Prefer using absolute paths in tool commands.
- Keep templates and Python code ASCII-only unless existing content requires Unicode.
- Use HTMX best practices: specify `hx-target` and `hx-swap` explicitly on dynamic triggers.
- Default to HTMX interactions instead of custom JavaScript or AJAX when enhancing views.
- Favor Bootstrap components and utility classes before introducing custom CSS.
- Activate `/Users/zdanozdan/workspace/regalator/venv` before invoking Django `manage.py` commands.
